summary:
Harry Styles, Malibu; 02/09/2018💛
Imagine.🌼
You spent last night together, eating pizza on the sofa and listening to ‘80s music...
body:
Harry Styles, Malibu; 02/09/2018💛

Imagine.🌼

You spent last night together, eating pizza on the sofa and listening to ‘80s music while he kissed you slowly and soft and made love bites on your neck, making love for all the night. You wore his t-shirt and his men shorts because you didn’t plan this love-week. Now he’s buying your healthy breakfast, dressed like this and using your hair clip to hold his hair and a bandana. You are spending the rest of the day on his private beach, eating sandwiches made by him, playing stupid water games and listening to his sweet and delicate compliments.

body: I’m crying they’ve all come so far, Harry has an album all hipsters love and has had a sold-out world tour doing some shows as big as 1d as well as starring as an actor in a Christopher Nolan film, Louis is a judge on X factor mentoring others and is currently working on his album and also has radio hits, Niall has a full album radio hits and is currently on a world tour and has an incredible girlfriend and Liam he just released his first ep and is working on an album along with so many radios hits, to think all of this came from some average auditions that happened on the X-factor 8 years ago, they’ve all worked incredibly hard to get to where they are now and I’m so incredibly proud.
